attributes.name: I just want to know more about the Journey

field_step_body.value:
Journey - Built by Morpht

The Journey can be easily managed in the GovCMS backend.

It is built to utilise the Taxonomy system, requires no external modules and can be customised easily.

No additional training is required, anyone familiar with Drupal or GovCMS can build a journey!
